OL,3,CCulture Secretary: Racism experienced
OL,4,Cby Jess Carter is 'horrifying'
OL,6,FThe Culture Secretary Lisa Nandy has
OL,7,Ftold ITV News the online racism
OL,8,Fexperienced by Jess Carter during the
OL,9,FEuros was "horrendous", adding that
OL,10,F"this has to be the moment that acts
OL,11,Fas a catalyst for change".
OL,13,FIn an interview with ITV News Sports
OL,14,FEditor Steve Scott, the Lioness said
OL,15,Fwas targeted by "violently aggressive
OL,16,Fracism" online.
