OL,3,CCulture Secretary: Racism experienced
OL,4,Cby Jess Carter is 'horrifying'
OL,6,FThe night before the final against
OL,7,FSpain, Carter said it was the first
OL,8,Ftime she had ever "been scared to
OL,9,Fplay" because of "whatever abuse might
OL,10,Fcome with it".
OL,12,FIn response, Nandy said it was
OL,13,F"horrifying" to hear the racism that
OL,14,FCarter had received.
OL,16,F"I don't want the next generation of
OL,17,FJess Carter's to be put off from
OL,18,Fplaying football because of the
OL,19,Fexperience that she and others have
OL,20,Fhad to go through," she said.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G2/10
OL,2,W,.!/  +.!/*%*%R,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
