OL,6,F"So her speaking out has to be the
OL,7,Fmoment when we all get a wakeup call
OL,8,Fand we say enough is enough."
OL,10,F"It's horrendous that it's happening
OL,11,Fin plain sight"
OL,13,FNandy said she had a "tremendous
OL,14,Famount of admiration" for Carter for
OL,15,Fspeaking out, however added that it
OL,16,Fshouldn't be up to her and other
OL,17,Fplayers to "fight these battles alone".
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G3/10
