OL,3,CCulture Secretary: Racism experienced
OL,4,Cby Jess Carter is 'horrifying'
OL,6,FShe said the government had set up a
OL,7,FWomen's Sport Taskforce since the
OL,8,FLionesses' success, to ensure what
OL,9,FCarter has experienced "no longer"
OL,10,Fhappens in sport.
OL,12,FShe also added that the government has
OL,13,Fpassed legislation placing tougher
OL,14,Fstandards on social media companies,
OL,15,Fwith a requirement to take down
OL,16,Fharmful content quickly, and that
OL,17,FTechnology Secretary Peter Kyle was
OL,18,Flooking at what more the government
OL,19,Fcan do.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G4/10
