OL,3,CCulture Secretary: Racism experienced
OL,4,Cby Jess Carter is 'horrifying'
OL,6,FShe continued: "We've got to get to
OL,7,Fthe point where, as a society, we are
OL,8,Fasserting the right of young women,
OL,9,Fwhatever their race, whatever their
OL,10,Fbackground, to go out and to
OL,11,Fparticipate in sports at the highest
OL,12,Flevel, and face nothing but
OL,13,Fcelebration for their talent."
OL,15,F"This has to be the moment that acts
OL,16,Fas a catalyst for change, where we say
OL,17,F'we won't tolerate this anymore'," she
OL,18,Fadded.
