OL,4,Cby Jess Carter is 'horrifying'
OL,6,FKemi Badenoch said it was
OL,7,F"heartbreaking" to hear Jess Carter
OL,8,Fspeak about the racism she received
OL,10,F"But there are certain groups of
OL,11,Fpeople who target very high profile
OL,12,Fethnic minorities. They're not many,
OL,13,Fbut they're able to do so publicly and
OL,14,Fvisibly.
OL,16,F"The targeting of specific individuals
OL,17,Fmeans that even though there's not
OL,18,Fthat much racism in the country,
OL,19,Fspecific individuals can actually feel
OL,20,Fquite a lot of it.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G8/10
