OL,6,F"And that's what Jess is saying, so
OL,7,FI'm not surprised by what she has
OL,8,Fsaid."
OL,10,FBadenoch said that everyone needs to
OL,11,Freinforce that the UK is a "country
OL,12,Fthat doesn't judge people on the
OL,13,Fcolour of their skin, or their sex,
OL,14,Ftheir gender.
OL,16,F"We are a country that judges people
OL,17,Fbased on how good they are, what they
OL,18,Fdo, what they can achieve, their
OL,19,Fpotential."
